              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-activations"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Initiate the email verification process.\n    \n- **Function**: Generates and sends a numeric OTP to the user's registered email to confirm ownership and activate the account."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Activation Account Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\r\n     \"code\": \"224256\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/account-activations/verify",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-activations",
                "verify"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Confirm account ownership.\n    \n- **Function**: Validates the OTP provided by the user. If correct, the account status is updated to \"Active.\""
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Reset Password Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/account-resets",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-resets"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Request a password recovery for forgotten Password.\n    \n- **Function**: Verifies the existence of the email and sends a secure reset code to allow the user to bypass the old password"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Reset Password Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\r\n    \"code\": \"760800\",\r\n    \"newPassword\": \"{{user_reset_password}}\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/account-resets/verify",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-resets",
                "verify"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Authorize the password reset.\n    \n- **Function**: Validates the recovery code and its expiration. Upon success, it grants the user permission to set a new password.\n    \n- This action performs a **Global Logout**. It will immediately invalidate every active session (Mobile, Web, etc.) by clearing all **Refresh Tokens** and rotating the **Security Stamp**. Any existing **Access Token** will be rejected on the next request."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Change Password code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/account-passwordchanges",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-passwordchanges"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Request a security-based password update.\n    \n- **Function**: Sends a verification code to ensure the user requesting the change is the actual account owner, often used as a Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) step."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Change Password Code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\r\n    \"code\": \"325548\",\r\n    \"newPassword\": \"{{user_password}}\",\r\n    \"oldPassword\": \"{{user_reset_password}}\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/account-passwordchanges/verify",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "account-passwordchanges",
                "verify"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- **Description**: Finalize the password update.\n    \n- **Function**: Validates the code and updates the `PasswordHash` in the database with the newly provided password.\n    \n- This action performs a **Global Logout**. It will immediately invalidate every active session (Mobile, Web, etc.) by clearing all **Refresh Tokens** and rotating the **Security Stamp**. Any existing **Access Token** will be rejected on the next request."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {\r",
                  "    var response = pm.response.json();\r",
                  "    \r",
                  "    \r",
                  "    if (response.data && response.data.token) {\r",
                  "        pm.environment.set(\"token\", response.data.token);  \r",
                  "    }\r",
                  "\r",
                  "    if (response.data && response.data.refreshToken) {\r",
                  "        pm.environment.set(\"refresh_token\", response.data.refreshToken);  \r",
                  "    }\r",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n  \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\r\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "- Authenticate user and send a **JWT (Access Token)** along with a **Refresh Token**.\n    \n- **Function**: Validates credentials against the database and returns a **JWT (JSON Web Token)** for authorization and a **Refresh Token** for session persistence if the account is active. This allows the client to renew the Access Token without requiring the user to re-enter their password."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {\r",
                  "    var response = pm.response.json();\r",
                  "    \r",
                  "    \r",
                  "    if (response.data && response.data.token) {\r",
                  "        pm.environment.set(\"token\", response.data.token);  \r",
                  "    }\r",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n  \"refreshToken\": \"RWAfLhXi2nIiWH0ALQ6GtZFu3y8BaGtX68UYCFwd4BmEtz2CrfKXZ5OUqbnkD1uyMLmPlw4Jy1pRIJKAQmF7UA==\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/accounts/refresh-token",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "accounts",
                "refresh-token"
              ]
            },
            "description": "### **1\\. Description**\n\nExchange an expired **JWT (Access Token)** for a new one using a **Refresh Token**.\n\n---\n\n### **2\\. Function**\n\nValidates the provided **Refresh Token** against the database and returns a new **JWT (JSON Web Token)** for authorization and a new **Refresh Token** for session persistence if the account is active. This allows the client to renew the Access Token without requiring the user to re-enter their password, while implementing **Token Rotation** for enhanced security."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "The **Guest Panel** is a collection of public endpoints that do not require an authorization token for access. It handles the initial user journey, including account creation, identity verification through One-Time Passwords (OTP), and secure authenticationز"
