            "description": "Description: Retrieves a paginated and searchable list of all registered users. This endpoint is designed for administrative oversight, allowing managers to filter through the user base efficiently.\n\nKey Features:\n\nAccess Control: Restricted to users with Admin or Manager roles.\n\nSearch: Multi-word search across UserName and Email fields (Case-insensitive).\n\nSorting: Supports dynamic sorting by Name or Email in both ascending and descending order.\n\nSmart Pagination: Returns total count, page size, and total pages to facilitate frontend pagination controls.\n\nDynamic Messaging: Provides contextual feedback if the list is empty or if the requested page exceeds the total count.\n\nQuery Parameters:\n\n<img src=\"https://content.pstmn.io/c5ea6014-f83c-4538-b8a1-a2288faeb053/aW1hZ2UucG5n\" alt=\"\" height=\"281\" width=\"785\">\n\nAuth: Requires a valid Admin/Manager JWT."
